Mamelodi Sundowns defender Motjeka Madisha has died in a car crash. The 25-year-old died in a car crash in Kempton Park, just hours after his team hosted a gala dinner. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Mamelodi Sundowns defender, Motjeka Madisha, has died. The 25-year-old died in a car crash in Kempton Park on Saturday night, just hours after his team hosted a gala dinner. WATCH: Anele Ngcongca laid to rest The Ekurhuleni Disaster Management officials were the first to respond. Spokesperson William Ntladihas shared harrowing details about what they saw at the scene of the accident. Watch the video above.